Bonus Fact:
• Just for fun, we also ran this experiment

00:12:34.290 --> 00:12:38.019
on cans of Dr. Pepper to see if the results
changed at all.

00:12:38.019 --> 00:12:41.050
They did not in terms of the main points already
made.

00:12:41.050 --> 00:12:45.070
However, what was interesting to note was
that the Dr. Pepper produced about half as

00:12:45.070 --> 00:12:49.089
much foam on average as the Coca-Cola for
